WEBVTT

00:11.602 --> 00:15.506
[ static, overlapping
radio transmissions ]

00:17.000 --> 00:23.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:31.004 --> 00:33.506
[ siren ]

00:34.407 --> 00:37.694
[ engine accelerating ]

00:37.694 --> 00:39.830
[ muffled car horn passes ]

01:03.420 --> 01:04.870
[ tires screech ]

01:06.557 --> 01:08.659
[ car horn honking ]

01:13.046 --> 01:14.214
[ horn blares ]

01:18.969 --> 01:20.804
[ horn blares ]

01:27.544 --> 01:30.647
[ tires screech ]

01:34.367 --> 01:35.719
[ tires screech ]

01:51.418 --> 01:52.986
[ second siren ]

01:54.371 --> 01:55.905
[ tires screech ]

01:58.258 --> 01:59.527
[ truck horn honks ]

02:00.510 --> 02:02.278
[ truck horn honks ]

02:03.479 --> 02:05.449
[ truck horn honks ]

02:09.469 --> 02:12.072
[ airplane takes off ]

02:25.618 --> 02:26.854
ANGELICA: [ on cell phone ]
It's late.

02:26.854 --> 02:28.221
MICHAEL:
I know. I'm sorry.

02:28.221 --> 02:29.556
Is everything okay?

02:29.556 --> 02:33.426
No, no, there was
this mechanical issue
with the plane,

02:33.426 --> 02:34.695
and we were delayed,

02:34.695 --> 02:37.965
and then customs,
it just--it took forever.

02:37.965 --> 02:40.367
This is hard, Michael.
There's history.

02:40.367 --> 02:41.869
You know I want this
to work.

02:41.869 --> 02:45.205
It's just you coming.
I don't know.

02:45.205 --> 02:47.274
Angie, just listen to me.

02:47.274 --> 02:49.209
I'm here, okay?

02:49.209 --> 02:51.644
And it's gonna be
different this time,

02:51.644 --> 02:52.746
I promise.

02:52.746 --> 02:54.281
I want to believe that.

02:54.281 --> 02:56.149
You know, I really do.

02:56.149 --> 02:59.519
Just please don't
let me down again, okay?

02:59.519 --> 03:01.554
I'll be waiting.

03:01.554 --> 03:04.057
Okay. I'll see you
in 20 minutes.

03:04.057 --> 03:05.726
Okay.

03:05.726 --> 03:07.160
[ cell phone beeps ]

03:15.668 --> 03:17.837
[ alarm chirps,
doors unlock ]

03:33.587 --> 03:35.088
[ sighs ]

03:48.201 --> 03:50.771
[ dialing ]

03:55.541 --> 03:57.393
Hertz Rental,
Sandy speaking.

03:57.393 --> 03:58.528
How may I help you?

03:58.528 --> 03:59.730
Yeah,
this is Michael Woods.

03:59.730 --> 04:00.831
I was just in there
a moment ago.

04:00.831 --> 04:02.565
Oh, yes, the American.
Mm-hmm.

04:02.565 --> 04:03.934
Is everything okay,
Mr. Woods?

04:03.934 --> 04:06.402
No, actually, uh
this is a minivan.

04:06.402 --> 04:07.804
I ordered a sedan.

04:07.804 --> 04:09.605
Um, well, why don't you
just come back on in,

04:09.605 --> 04:11.341
and we'll see if we can't
find out what the problem is.

04:11.341 --> 04:12.926
I'm sure my manager
will be back any time.

04:12.926 --> 04:14.410
You can't sort this out?

04:14.410 --> 04:15.846
No, sir.

04:15.846 --> 04:17.113
I'm afraid I'm not
that good with a computer,

04:17.113 --> 04:19.249
but my manager will be back
anytime soon now.

04:19.249 --> 04:21.517
You know what?
This is gonna be fine.

04:21.517 --> 04:23.219
No, no, no, sir.
Yeah.

04:23.219 --> 04:24.520
I'm sorry to say--

04:24.520 --> 04:26.056
Unfortunately,
I'm running late.

04:26.056 --> 04:27.858
Somebody's
waiting for me,

04:27.858 --> 04:29.926
and we'll just sort it
out when I come back,
all right?

04:29.926 --> 04:31.177
No, sir. I'm afraid
you don't understand--

04:31.177 --> 04:32.746
Thank you. Bye.

04:41.421 --> 04:42.388
This is weird.

05:23.463 --> 05:24.848
What?

05:31.705 --> 05:33.307
[ horn honks,
tires screech ]

05:41.398 --> 05:43.065
They drive on the left.

05:43.065 --> 05:46.836
[ "Go Away"
by Teargas playing ]

06:43.760 --> 06:48.481
[ man shouting ]

07:03.530 --> 07:05.081
[ cell phone beeps ]

07:32.575 --> 07:34.311
[ child laughing ]

08:19.522 --> 08:21.224
[ car horn honks ]

08:21.224 --> 08:25.028
[ many cars honking ]

08:28.564 --> 08:30.200
[ thud ]
MAN: Hey!

08:33.253 --> 08:34.837
I'm sorry.

08:34.837 --> 08:36.606
I'm sorry, man!

08:42.511 --> 08:44.965
Better wake up!

08:44.965 --> 08:47.501
Stay out of trouble,
Michael.

08:47.501 --> 08:49.068
Stay out of trouble.

08:50.169 --> 08:53.573
Stay out of trouble,
stay out of trouble.

09:01.898 --> 09:04.066
[ line ringing ]

09:05.718 --> 09:07.087
Hey.

09:07.087 --> 09:08.521
ANGELICA:
Where are you?

09:08.521 --> 09:11.324
I'm...I'm stuck
in a traffic jam.

09:11.324 --> 09:13.059
There must be an accident
or something,

09:13.059 --> 09:16.362
and then I ran
into an issue with the
rental car company, too.

09:16.362 --> 09:18.464
Michael, you know
what security is like here.

09:18.464 --> 09:20.133
Just to get
this little bit of time,

09:20.133 --> 09:22.002
I have to go through
a whole procedure.

09:22.002 --> 09:23.369
No, I know, I know,

09:23.369 --> 09:24.670
but, I mean,
it's not my fault.

09:24.670 --> 09:26.139
What am I
supposed to do?

09:26.139 --> 09:28.307
I can't control the air
flow or the traffic.

09:28.307 --> 09:30.227
I mean, can't you just
wait for a little bit?

09:30.227 --> 09:31.928
I've been waiting
for 18 months.

09:31.928 --> 09:33.530
I know.

09:33.530 --> 09:35.298
All right,
and I'm here now.

09:35.298 --> 09:37.784
When the parole board
approved your travel,

09:37.784 --> 09:41.154
I thought this could be
like a new start for us,

09:41.154 --> 09:42.355
[ crying ]
but now I'm scared that...

09:42.355 --> 09:44.190
What? Wait,
why are you crying?

09:44.190 --> 09:45.826
No more stories, Michael.

09:45.826 --> 09:47.060
I can't get hurt again.

09:47.060 --> 09:48.895
What...
I can't.

09:48.895 --> 09:49.996
What stories?

09:49.996 --> 09:51.781
Did you stop
at the liquor store?

09:51.781 --> 09:53.466
No, come on, I told you.

09:53.466 --> 09:55.935
I'm stuck
in a traffic jam.

09:55.935 --> 09:57.403
Okay.

09:57.403 --> 10:00.539
Angie, just give me
this one chance, all right?

10:00.539 --> 10:03.109
I promise you
I'm not gonna screw it up.

10:05.544 --> 10:08.682
Okay. Okay,
call me when you get here.

10:10.650 --> 10:11.685
[ beep ]

10:30.153 --> 10:33.356
[ panting ]

10:37.977 --> 10:39.596
[ sighs ]

10:56.863 --> 10:58.497
[ cell phone chiming ]

11:00.683 --> 11:02.518
[ chiming ]

11:16.265 --> 11:18.684
[ horns starting to honk ]

11:23.056 --> 11:25.641
[ horn blares ]

11:27.878 --> 11:30.479
[ horns honking ]

11:32.215 --> 11:35.018
Hey, you'll
get there, buddy!

11:35.018 --> 11:36.653
God.

11:58.941 --> 12:00.242
[ tapping ]

12:07.116 --> 12:08.417
Hello, my friend.

12:08.417 --> 12:10.186
I'm selling chargers,
my friend.

12:10.186 --> 12:11.387
Yeah, I don't need
a charger.

12:11.387 --> 12:13.322
No, my friend.
Take a charger, my friend

12:13.322 --> 12:14.608
No, I just bought one
at the airport, though.

12:14.608 --> 12:15.725
Oh, come on,
those are cheap.

12:15.725 --> 12:17.259
They break all the time,
my friend.

12:17.259 --> 12:19.295
I don't need one.
No, my friend. Look at me.

12:19.295 --> 12:20.479
I'm the cutest boy
in town.

12:20.479 --> 12:21.547
Yeah, I'm sure you are.

12:21.547 --> 12:23.150
Which one do you use,
my friend?

12:23.150 --> 12:25.068
Hey, hey,
what are you do--

12:25.068 --> 12:26.936
MICHAEL:
Hey, what are you doing?

12:30.473 --> 12:32.575
They just stole my glasses.

12:35.928 --> 12:37.597
RADIO REPORTER: The big story
on Eyewitness News today

12:37.597 --> 12:39.499
is the disappearance
of the lead prosecutor

12:39.499 --> 12:41.867
in the case against
the Chief of Police, Ben Rose.

12:41.867 --> 12:44.804
Rachel Shabangu has been missing
for the past 24 hours,

12:44.804 --> 12:46.739
and her family and the NPA
have been pointing fingers

12:46.739 --> 12:48.375
at those implicated
in the case

12:48.375 --> 12:50.343
she was to provide
evidence against.

12:50.343 --> 12:52.478
SECOND REPORTER:
Alex, this is the third time

12:52.478 --> 12:55.281
that this kind of thing
has happened

12:55.281 --> 12:57.917
in a case
against the Chief of Police.

12:57.917 --> 12:59.853
FIRST REPORTER:
Well, the prosecutors here,

12:59.853 --> 13:02.521
they've seen this sort of thing
occurring on a regular basis.

13:02.521 --> 13:04.857
It seems like a blatant
disregard for the law

13:04.857 --> 13:07.660
by the very people
who are meant to uphold it.

13:25.694 --> 13:29.783
[ men laughing ]

13:47.900 --> 13:49.769
[ stops engine ]

13:55.792 --> 13:58.962
[ dog barking ]

14:03.933 --> 14:06.035
[ cell phone ringing ]

14:09.038 --> 14:12.274
[ ringing ]

14:14.376 --> 14:16.278
[ ringing ]

14:16.278 --> 14:17.847
[ stops ]

14:27.089 --> 14:30.426
[ ringing ]

14:31.394 --> 14:32.628
[ ringing ]

14:32.628 --> 14:34.197
Hello?

14:34.197 --> 14:37.466
MAN: You were meant
to acknowledge receipt
of the message.

14:37.466 --> 14:38.734
Hello, who is this?

14:38.734 --> 14:40.870
Can you tell me
what's going on here?

14:42.105 --> 14:43.339
Hello?

14:43.339 --> 14:45.708
How did you get
this phone?

14:45.708 --> 14:48.211
Uh...
it was in the glove box.

14:48.211 --> 14:50.046
[ stammers ] I...

14:50.046 --> 14:52.748
I picked up this car
from the rental car company.

14:52.748 --> 14:54.918
They screwed up the car
and...

14:54.918 --> 14:57.353
[ beep ]

14:57.353 --> 14:59.555
Hello?

15:01.958 --> 15:03.426
Hello?!

15:03.426 --> 15:05.929
Why is this gun
in my car?!

15:10.734 --> 15:11.935
Oh.

15:11.935 --> 15:13.369
[ dog barking ]

15:30.036 --> 15:31.837
To hell with this.

15:31.837 --> 15:33.872
I'm outta here.

15:59.832 --> 16:02.669
[ ringing ]

16:04.437 --> 16:07.773
[ ringing ]

16:09.509 --> 16:12.678
[ ringing ]

16:14.947 --> 16:19.035
[ ringing ]

16:20.086 --> 16:21.504
Hey.
MAN: Hello, Michael.

16:21.504 --> 16:22.671
Yeah, I just thought
you should know,

16:22.671 --> 16:23.873
I'm not playing
your stupid game.

16:23.873 --> 16:24.791
I'm outta here.

16:24.791 --> 16:26.075
I left your van,
your gun, your phone.

16:26.075 --> 16:27.410
Michael...
You can have it all, buddy.

16:27.410 --> 16:29.245
My name
is Detective Smith.

16:29.245 --> 16:33.116
We're in the middle
of a covert operation
at the airport.

16:33.116 --> 16:34.683
There was a mix-up.

16:34.683 --> 16:36.085
That car was meant
to be picked up

16:36.085 --> 16:38.387
by one of our undercover
police officers.

16:38.387 --> 16:41.524
We appreciate that this
was just a random mistake

16:41.524 --> 16:43.559
and that you are
an innocent party in this.

16:43.559 --> 16:46.178
That's good.
That's good news.

16:46.178 --> 16:48.280
You're not to blame here.
We know what happened.

16:48.280 --> 16:49.749
You have no idea.

16:49.749 --> 16:50.983
Yeah, well,
sorry about that.

16:50.983 --> 16:52.952
We've got another car
for you,

16:52.952 --> 16:54.386
so we'll send
you the address,

16:54.386 --> 16:55.988
and we can swap it
over, okay?

16:55.988 --> 16:58.825
Okay, great.

16:58.825 --> 17:00.927
That's a relief.
I got to...

17:00.927 --> 17:02.544
[ beep ]

17:02.544 --> 17:05.147
[ chimes ]

17:09.550 --> 17:12.421
[ starts engine ]

17:12.421 --> 17:15.457
Guess I'm not walking
after all.

17:15.457 --> 17:17.358
Uh, Smuts Street, please.

17:17.358 --> 17:18.527
MALE OPERATOR: Which one?

17:18.527 --> 17:20.896
I have over 57
in the directory, sir.

17:20.896 --> 17:24.300
Uh, I don't know.
I'm American.

17:24.300 --> 17:26.117
I'm not from here.

17:26.117 --> 17:27.887
Unfortunately, I cannot
help unless you have
more information.

17:27.887 --> 17:28.921
Goodbye.

17:28.921 --> 17:31.190
[ beep ]

17:31.190 --> 17:33.459
[ man shouting ]

17:33.459 --> 17:37.229
[ man and woman
conversing in Zulu ]

17:39.432 --> 17:41.934
Excuse me. Excuse me.

17:41.934 --> 17:44.069
Could you tell me
where Smuts Street is?

17:44.069 --> 17:46.171
[ speaking Zulu ]

17:46.171 --> 17:48.541
Right. Uh-huh.

17:48.541 --> 17:51.043
[ speaking Zulu ]

17:51.043 --> 17:53.212
Could have seen
that one coming.

17:53.212 --> 17:57.617
[ "Stand Up"
by Perfecto playing ]

18:01.537 --> 18:03.539
Smuts.

18:03.539 --> 18:06.175
Smuts Street.

18:06.175 --> 18:08.978
[ song continues ]

18:11.580 --> 18:12.765
Excuse me.

18:14.934 --> 18:18.003
Uh, it's all right.
Never mind. Thank you.

19:03.265 --> 19:05.217
[ song ends ]

19:09.255 --> 19:11.124
I got to turn around.

19:11.124 --> 19:12.525
[ thud ]

19:12.525 --> 19:14.576
Crap.

19:19.882 --> 19:22.784
[ engine revving ]

19:27.056 --> 19:28.758
[ stops engine ]

19:39.218 --> 19:43.172
[ dialing ]

19:43.172 --> 19:45.174
[ line ringing ]

19:46.542 --> 19:48.210
[ ringing ]

19:49.611 --> 19:51.013
ANGELICA:
What's going on?

19:51.013 --> 19:52.782
You're
half an hour late.

19:52.782 --> 19:55.717
Yeah, I got...

19:55.717 --> 19:58.687
I got lost,
and now I'm stuck.

19:59.856 --> 20:01.657
Where are you?

20:01.657 --> 20:05.161
I turned off, uh...

20:05.161 --> 20:06.829
Crane Street.

20:06.829 --> 20:10.366
Crane Street? What are you
doing on Crane Street?

20:12.835 --> 20:14.303
There was a mess-up--

20:14.303 --> 20:17.807
There was a mess-up
with the rental car, and this...

20:17.807 --> 20:20.076
The wrong car?
I don't understand.

20:20.076 --> 20:21.944
[ sighs ]

20:23.545 --> 20:25.081
Michael?

20:27.850 --> 20:30.486
Angie, do you love me?

20:30.486 --> 20:31.753
What?

20:31.753 --> 20:33.022
You heard me.

20:35.091 --> 20:36.658
Michael, what's going on?

20:36.658 --> 20:39.428
Because
if you really love me,

20:39.428 --> 20:42.832
I need you to tell me
how to get to Smuts Street,

20:42.832 --> 20:46.702
and then I need you to not
ask me any more questions.

20:46.702 --> 20:48.570
And, please,
just give me 20 more--

20:48.570 --> 20:49.906
20 more minutes,

20:49.906 --> 20:51.440
and if I'm not there
within 20 minutes,

20:51.440 --> 20:54.043
you don't ever have
to talk to me again, okay?

21:01.216 --> 21:02.752
Go back.

21:05.621 --> 21:07.557
Go back on Crane,

21:07.557 --> 21:09.324
take a right on Gull,

21:09.324 --> 21:12.027
and then the third left
at the light is Smuts.

21:13.463 --> 21:14.764
All right.

21:14.764 --> 21:16.899
All right,
I love you.

21:18.634 --> 21:19.769
[ beep ]

21:23.706 --> 21:25.390
[ starts engine ]

21:27.593 --> 21:29.911
[ engine revving ]

21:36.619 --> 21:39.121
[ tires spinning ]

21:43.809 --> 21:46.962
[ thud, seat back falls ]

22:16.692 --> 22:18.528
I'm not gonna hurt you.
I swear to God.

22:23.865 --> 22:27.286
I'm gonna
take this gag off, okay?

22:33.008 --> 22:35.794
Are you all right?

22:36.828 --> 22:38.497
[ whispers ] Water.

22:38.497 --> 22:40.416
Water.
Yeah.

23:01.470 --> 23:03.772
Can you untie me?

23:03.772 --> 23:05.241
Yeah.

23:18.887 --> 23:19.872
Oh, sh--!

23:19.872 --> 23:22.908
[ gasping ]

23:24.593 --> 23:25.660
Are you crazy?

23:25.660 --> 23:27.513
Who are you?

23:27.513 --> 23:28.547
Who are you?

23:28.547 --> 23:30.215
Who are you?
Who are you?

23:30.215 --> 23:32.017
They wouldn't have left
this to some random guy,

23:32.017 --> 23:34.019
so don't play
the innocent man.

23:35.220 --> 23:37.372
You just sit back,
all right?

23:37.372 --> 23:39.024
I don't know what the hell
you're talking about,

23:39.024 --> 23:40.259
and I don't really care.

23:40.259 --> 23:41.577
You just sit there,
and you shut up.

23:41.577 --> 23:43.178
Just sit in your seat!

23:43.178 --> 23:46.065
Just stay there.
This is crazy!

23:57.876 --> 23:59.845
Oh, God.

24:36.599 --> 24:37.583
[ van rattles ]

24:39.601 --> 24:41.887
I'm gone.

24:49.111 --> 24:51.263
WOMAN:
Turn the car around.

24:52.781 --> 24:54.816
Turn the car around.

24:54.816 --> 24:56.301
I don't want to hear it.

24:56.301 --> 24:58.720
Listen to what I say,
and you won't get hurt.

24:58.720 --> 25:02.091
Turn the car around.

25:07.580 --> 25:09.948
I don't have anything
to do with this, all right?

25:09.948 --> 25:11.500
Not a thing.

25:11.500 --> 25:14.920
I don't have
any involvement in this.

25:17.038 --> 25:20.892
You're driving too fast.
Slow down.

25:23.612 --> 25:25.715
I said slow down!

25:25.715 --> 25:27.015
[ woman grunts ]

25:27.015 --> 25:28.250
[ bullet whistles ]

25:50.572 --> 25:51.741
Enough!

25:51.741 --> 25:52.775
Okay, okay, okay, okay.

25:52.775 --> 25:56.111
Okay. Okay. Okay.
Okay. Okay.

26:15.564 --> 26:17.716
[ wind whooshes ]
[ woman grunts ]

26:17.716 --> 26:19.618
What are you doing?

26:22.004 --> 26:24.990
[ horn blaring ]

26:31.914 --> 26:34.449
Stay in the car!
You stay in the car!

26:38.887 --> 26:41.273
You don't know
what you're doing.

26:43.775 --> 26:45.444
Sit down!

26:47.128 --> 26:52.701
You just don't--
[ cell phone ringing ]

26:52.701 --> 26:54.135
Hello?

26:54.135 --> 26:55.271
SMITH:
You're late, Michael Woods.

26:55.271 --> 26:56.605
Yeah, I know. I'm sorry.

26:56.605 --> 26:58.908
You got out of jail
only 10 days ago.

26:58.908 --> 27:00.675
I checked your record.

27:00.675 --> 27:03.478
Already broken
your parole condition
by leaving the country,

27:03.478 --> 27:05.180
an ex-wife
at the embassy.

27:05.180 --> 27:06.448
Is that
where you're going?

27:06.448 --> 27:08.517
No, no, I'm on my way
to you right now.

27:08.517 --> 27:10.920
Do you want to go back
to jail, Mr. Woods?

27:10.920 --> 27:12.254
No.
Five minutes,

27:12.254 --> 27:14.456
or we're coming for you.

27:14.456 --> 27:15.891
I'm coming.

27:15.891 --> 27:17.326
There's a woman--

27:17.326 --> 27:19.361
There's a woman
tied up in the back.
[ beep ]

27:19.361 --> 27:21.329
Hello?

27:24.916 --> 27:26.585
Ju--Just--

27:26.585 --> 27:29.088
Just stay
in your seat, please!

27:29.088 --> 27:30.589
Just stay in your seat,
all right?

27:30.589 --> 27:33.125
Just stay there.
Don't move, nothing!

27:33.125 --> 27:34.826
Just stay there.

27:57.266 --> 27:59.601
You don't know
what's going on, do you?

28:01.770 --> 28:04.606
I think I need to explain
the situation you
find yourself in.

28:04.606 --> 28:06.875
You're talking
to the wrong person.

28:06.875 --> 28:08.810
My name
is Rachel Shabangu.

28:08.810 --> 28:12.414
I work for the National
Prosecuting Authority.

28:12.414 --> 28:15.484
I've recently
uncovered information

28:15.484 --> 28:19.555
implicating
a very powerful man
named Ben Rose

28:19.555 --> 28:23.625
on various counts
of international sex
trafficking.

28:23.625 --> 28:25.994
The last thing
I remember
is going home,

28:25.994 --> 28:27.363
opening my front door,

28:27.363 --> 28:29.230
then waking up in
this minivan with you.

28:29.230 --> 28:31.567
I have reason
to believe I have
been kidnapped

28:31.567 --> 28:34.235
to prevent
this information
from coming to light.

28:34.235 --> 28:35.637
You know, I don't want
to hear any of this.

28:35.637 --> 28:37.072
All right? I don't
want to hear any of it.

28:37.072 --> 28:38.423
You have to
do the right thing.

28:38.423 --> 28:40.625
You know,
just save it, all right?

28:40.625 --> 28:42.344
You just save it
for the police.

28:42.344 --> 28:44.246
When we get there,
you can tell them all
about your story.

28:44.246 --> 28:46.398
Ben Rose
is the Chief of Police.

28:49.401 --> 28:52.504
It's the police
that want me dead.

28:58.143 --> 29:01.930
Look, I don't know
how you got involved
in this, but you are.

29:01.930 --> 29:03.548
No.

29:03.548 --> 29:04.900
This is my reality,
and it's just become yours.

29:04.900 --> 29:06.334
No, it hasn't
become my reality!

29:06.334 --> 29:07.770
You may not like it.
This isn't my reality!

29:07.770 --> 29:09.938
Sometimes life
doesn't give us a choice!

29:09.938 --> 29:11.106
I got to do
what I got to do!

29:11.106 --> 29:12.440
You're in this situation
for a reason!

29:12.440 --> 29:13.709
I just got to stay
out of trouble right now!

29:13.709 --> 29:14.543
You just shut up!

29:14.543 --> 29:15.528
You have to do
the right thing!

29:15.528 --> 29:16.861
No, I don't! You shut up!

29:16.861 --> 29:18.264
Don't you get it?
You cannot cut this out!

29:18.264 --> 29:19.881
I can't think straight! Aah!
You cannot--

30:00.989 --> 30:03.559
[ wings fluttering ]

30:11.282 --> 30:13.251
I guess this is right.

30:24.763 --> 30:25.848
[ gunshot ]

30:26.865 --> 30:28.584
Go! Go! Go!

30:28.584 --> 30:30.369
Why are they
shooting at us?

30:30.369 --> 30:32.170
Just get the hell out of here!
Go, go, go!

30:32.170 --> 30:33.505
I'm going, I'm going!

30:35.090 --> 30:36.491
[ tires screech ]

30:36.491 --> 30:38.460
Get back
onto the main road!

30:40.095 --> 30:41.597
Go, go, go, go, go!

30:41.597 --> 30:43.431
MICHAEL:
I'm going! I'm going!

30:48.804 --> 30:50.772
Give me the gun.

30:50.772 --> 30:51.807
Give me the gun!

30:51.807 --> 30:53.058
These people are
going to kill us!

30:53.058 --> 30:54.142
Give me the gun!

30:54.142 --> 30:55.494
[ gunshots ]

30:55.494 --> 30:56.661
Will you
give me the gun?

30:59.431 --> 31:00.865
[ gunshots ]

31:00.865 --> 31:02.000
Faster!

31:02.000 --> 31:04.269
[ gunshots ]

31:04.269 --> 31:06.305
[ glass breaking,
bullet ricochets ]

31:06.305 --> 31:08.207
Shoot them! Shoot them!

31:08.207 --> 31:09.591
Go faster! Go!

31:09.591 --> 31:11.276
I'm going! I'm going.
You have to go!

31:14.262 --> 31:15.597
Go!
I'm going!

31:15.597 --> 31:17.416
Move!

31:18.784 --> 31:20.753
Okay. Hey, hey!

31:20.753 --> 31:22.854
When I say you get inside,
you get inside, all right?

31:22.854 --> 31:24.172
What?

31:24.172 --> 31:25.474
When I say duck inside...
What?

31:25.474 --> 31:26.741
you duck inside!

31:32.447 --> 31:33.966
There's a wall!

31:33.966 --> 31:37.670
I know! When I say duck inside,
you get inside!

31:37.670 --> 31:38.520
Now!

32:31.740 --> 32:35.544
[ man singing somber song
indistinctly ]

33:04.139 --> 33:05.390
I know someone.

33:07.025 --> 33:08.960
Someone who can help.

33:14.182 --> 33:16.451
[ indistinct conversation
and laughter ]

33:22.524 --> 33:24.159
[ children laughing ]

33:27.378 --> 33:29.131
Where are we?

33:29.131 --> 33:30.565
It's a township.

33:30.565 --> 33:32.434
Just keep going
further down.

33:37.289 --> 33:39.507
All right,
turn right here.

33:43.679 --> 33:46.715
This is it. Wait here.

34:01.613 --> 34:04.349
[ no audible dialogue ]

34:04.349 --> 34:05.917
[ person whistling ]

34:11.505 --> 34:13.976
Can you just
talk to him?

34:24.386 --> 34:26.987
What's going on?

34:26.987 --> 34:29.690
We're gonna have
to try someone else.

34:37.833 --> 34:40.268
RACHEL:
There he is, there.

34:40.268 --> 34:41.601
Benji!

34:42.904 --> 34:43.972
Benji!

34:43.972 --> 34:45.806
MICHAEL:
Hey, Benji!

34:46.975 --> 34:48.176
Okay, go around.
He's ignoring us.

34:48.176 --> 34:49.244
Go around.

34:52.214 --> 34:54.148
There.

34:54.148 --> 34:55.516
Benji!

34:56.384 --> 34:57.836
Benji.

34:57.836 --> 35:01.522
[ speaks Zulu ]
They kidnapped me.

35:01.522 --> 35:02.557
They tried to kill us.

35:02.557 --> 35:06.227
[ speaking Zulu ]

35:06.227 --> 35:10.048
Benji... [ speaking Zulu ]

35:10.048 --> 35:14.602
[ speaking Zulu ]

35:14.602 --> 35:16.237
Benji!

35:23.444 --> 35:25.847
They threatened my son
at his school.

35:25.847 --> 35:28.133
You know what I'm saying?
At his school.

35:28.133 --> 35:31.302
He's only 8.

35:31.302 --> 35:34.172
Please leave me alone.

35:43.415 --> 35:45.550
They threatened his son.

35:45.550 --> 35:48.153
That means they're
gonna go after my wife.

35:48.153 --> 35:49.353
She's at the embassy.

35:49.353 --> 35:50.905
RACHEL:
Call her.

35:50.905 --> 35:53.357
Whatever happens,
she must stay where she is.

35:53.357 --> 35:57.028
[ dialing ]

35:57.028 --> 35:58.597
[ line ringing ]

35:58.597 --> 36:01.600
Hey, it's Angie.
You know what to do.

36:01.600 --> 36:02.767
[ beep ]

36:02.767 --> 36:05.337
Angie, listen,
I need you to stay put.

36:05.337 --> 36:06.605
I don't want you to move.

36:06.605 --> 36:07.772
I want you to stay
right where you're at.

36:07.772 --> 36:09.674
There's some guys that--

36:09.674 --> 36:11.275
Listen, just stay
where you are, all right?

36:11.275 --> 36:12.477
I'm on my way.

36:12.477 --> 36:14.195
I'm coming
to get you right now.

36:14.195 --> 36:16.164
You can't go there.

36:16.164 --> 36:17.532
I have to go there.

36:17.532 --> 36:18.967
You can't.

36:18.967 --> 36:20.569
That's exactly
where they're headed.

36:20.569 --> 36:23.021
These people
are dangerous,
and they will kill us.

36:23.021 --> 36:26.458
She's safe. They can't
get her at the embassy.

36:26.458 --> 36:29.027
I don't care. I'm going.

36:35.900 --> 36:38.036
Give me the phone.

36:44.125 --> 36:46.294
What department
at the embassy?

36:46.294 --> 36:47.929
Uh, Diplomatic, uh...

36:47.929 --> 36:49.130
Hey.

36:49.130 --> 36:50.631
It's on the phone.
Look on the phone.

36:50.631 --> 36:52.067
It's gonna be okay.

36:52.067 --> 36:55.170
She's safe there as long
as she stays inside.

36:55.170 --> 36:56.737
[ dialing ]

36:58.623 --> 37:01.576
[ line ringing ]

37:01.576 --> 37:03.044
WOMAN:
American Embassy.

37:03.044 --> 37:06.231
Yes, hi, can I have
Diplomatic Affairs, please?

37:06.231 --> 37:07.699
Not a problem, ma'am.

37:07.699 --> 37:09.617
Who would you
like to speak to?

37:09.617 --> 37:12.637
I'm looking for Angelica...

37:12.637 --> 37:14.755
Moore, Angelica Moore.

37:14.755 --> 37:16.458
Angelica Moore, please.

37:16.458 --> 37:19.127
WOMAN: I'm sorry.
She just stepped out.

37:19.127 --> 37:20.628
How long ago?

37:20.628 --> 37:21.930
[ indistinct reply ]

37:21.930 --> 37:22.964
What?

37:22.964 --> 37:24.165
RACHEL:
She just stepped out.

37:24.165 --> 37:25.934
There was someone
to see her.

37:25.934 --> 37:28.169
Put on your seatbelt.

37:29.637 --> 37:32.207
It's only a block away
off Nicol.

37:36.811 --> 37:39.780
[ tires screech ]

37:42.350 --> 37:44.119
It's red.

37:44.119 --> 37:45.053
It's red!

37:46.671 --> 37:48.857
[ tires screech ]

37:56.964 --> 37:59.100
RACHEL:
It's just there.

37:59.100 --> 38:00.351
There!

38:00.351 --> 38:02.520
Those are his men!

38:02.520 --> 38:03.989
Wait, there she is!

38:03.989 --> 38:05.974
There she is!
Get back inside!
[ honking horn ]

38:05.974 --> 38:07.625
Angie!
Michael!

38:07.625 --> 38:09.210
[ tires screech ]

38:11.445 --> 38:12.580
[ gunshots ]

38:12.580 --> 38:13.831
[ Rachel groans ]

38:13.831 --> 38:15.066
[ gunshots ]

38:18.603 --> 38:19.871
She got back in!

38:19.871 --> 38:21.206
She got back in!

38:21.206 --> 38:22.540
[ gasping ]

38:22.540 --> 38:24.309
You've been shot?

38:25.693 --> 38:28.429
Where's--We got to
get you to a hospital!

38:28.429 --> 38:31.499
No, no doctors.

38:31.499 --> 38:32.800
No hospitals.

38:32.800 --> 38:35.486
They'll find us.

38:35.486 --> 38:38.122
Turn...Turn here.

38:38.122 --> 38:39.224
Left here?

38:39.224 --> 38:40.391
Turn left.

38:40.391 --> 38:42.944
Go to that--that
underground parking sign.

38:42.944 --> 38:47.299
There. There. Right there.

38:48.950 --> 38:50.952
We can't
just stay down here.

38:52.136 --> 38:55.173
Okay, go down
to the bottom level.

38:59.711 --> 39:02.797
Find a place
out of sight,

39:02.797 --> 39:05.851
somewhere where
they can't see us.

39:08.736 --> 39:10.404
MICHAEL: Here.

39:16.678 --> 39:18.946
Okay. All right.

39:20.598 --> 39:21.632
I have
to take this off.

39:21.632 --> 39:23.601
I need you...
I need you...

39:23.601 --> 39:24.668
Help me get this off.

39:24.668 --> 39:27.638
I need
to see the wound.

39:27.638 --> 39:29.224
All right.

39:30.391 --> 39:32.494
[ groans ]

39:36.531 --> 39:37.699
This is it. Stop it.

39:37.699 --> 39:40.001
All right.

39:40.001 --> 39:42.870
You're gonna...okay.

39:42.870 --> 39:46.174
You're gonna
have to push harder.

39:46.174 --> 39:48.643
Just do it, push.
I'm pushing.

39:48.643 --> 39:50.578
Push harder.
I'm pushing.

39:50.578 --> 39:53.297
[ whimpering ]

39:55.266 --> 39:56.300
[ grunts ]

39:56.300 --> 39:57.669
It's not stopping.

39:57.669 --> 39:59.237
Come on.

40:01.122 --> 40:03.758
I'm not gonna make it.

40:03.758 --> 40:06.694
There's too much blood.

40:06.694 --> 40:09.196
There's too much blood.
It's not gonna happen.

40:09.196 --> 40:10.898
No, you're gonna be fine.

40:10.898 --> 40:12.066
It's not gonna happen.

40:12.066 --> 40:13.267
No, you're gonna be fine.
No.

40:13.267 --> 40:14.636
Come on.
There's too much.

40:14.636 --> 40:16.404
Watch out.
There's too much.

40:16.404 --> 40:17.739
It's not gonna...

40:17.739 --> 40:19.441
You hang in there.
I can't.

40:19.441 --> 40:20.442
You hang in there.

40:20.442 --> 40:21.242
I can't.

40:21.242 --> 40:23.010
You stay with me.
Come on.

40:27.499 --> 40:31.069
Give me your phone.
Get your phone.

40:33.872 --> 40:35.306
It records?

40:35.306 --> 40:36.791
Yeah.

40:36.791 --> 40:38.910
Turn it on.

40:41.712 --> 40:43.681
All right, just tap that.

40:43.681 --> 40:45.616
Hit that button.

40:45.616 --> 40:46.818
Push it.

40:46.818 --> 40:48.887
Push it?
Mm-hmm.

40:53.825 --> 40:57.095
My name
is Rachel Shabangu.

40:59.865 --> 41:06.954
Today,
October 12, 2011...

41:06.954 --> 41:09.291
I have been shot.

41:10.625 --> 41:14.562
In the event
that I don't survive,

41:14.562 --> 41:20.134
this will serve
as testimony
for my prosecution.

41:24.772 --> 41:29.577
On September 17, 2011...

41:31.813 --> 41:38.353
I uncovered
a sex trafficking ring
out of Johannesburg...

41:39.920 --> 41:42.707
It's okay.

41:42.707 --> 41:46.344
and a tail
that led back to

41:46.344 --> 41:53.518
Chief of Police...
Ben Rose.

41:58.773 --> 42:02.027
When I re--

42:02.027 --> 42:06.180
realized how deep
not only he,

42:06.180 --> 42:11.785
but other--other high-ranking
officers were involved,

42:11.785 --> 42:14.788
I tried--I tried to contact

42:14.788 --> 42:18.192
Judge James Mzuka...

42:22.030 --> 42:24.732
but then found myself...

42:31.105 --> 42:33.307
Concludes...

42:34.175 --> 42:36.577
my testimony...

42:38.713 --> 42:42.700
witnessed by...

42:44.201 --> 42:46.137
Michael, Michael Woods.

42:46.137 --> 42:50.208
Michael...Woods.

42:55.546 --> 42:56.931
No, open your eyes.

42:56.931 --> 42:58.116
Open your eyes.

42:58.116 --> 42:59.250
Hey, open your eyes.

42:59.250 --> 43:01.202
I want you to stay
with me, okay?

43:01.202 --> 43:02.403
I don't want this
on my shoulders.

43:02.403 --> 43:03.354
You're gonna stay with me,

43:03.354 --> 43:04.622
so I want
you just to breathe.

43:06.524 --> 43:09.627
Take it to...

43:09.627 --> 43:10.711
the courthouse.

43:11.996 --> 43:13.348
No, I'm not--
To the courthouse.

43:13.348 --> 43:15.433
I'm not gonna deal
with the police, okay?

43:15.433 --> 43:16.784
I'm not even
supposed to be here.

43:16.784 --> 43:17.868
You're gonna stay with me.

43:17.868 --> 43:23.974
Find...Judge...Mzuka.

43:23.974 --> 43:26.010
He's the only one

43:26.010 --> 43:27.312
you can trust.

43:27.312 --> 43:28.930
No, I'm not...
To the courthouse.

43:28.930 --> 43:31.349
You stay with me.
Just stay--Just--

43:31.349 --> 43:34.619
He's the only
one you can trust,

43:34.619 --> 43:36.087
no one else.

43:36.087 --> 43:38.356
No, I'm not trusting anybody.
You understand?

43:38.356 --> 43:40.425
You're gonna stay
right here, okay?

43:40.425 --> 43:42.026
You're gonna take it
to the judge.

43:42.026 --> 43:43.395
You're gonna do this.
You're gonna be fine.

43:43.395 --> 43:44.929
You're gonna
be fine, okay?

43:44.929 --> 43:46.113
You're gonna be fine.

43:46.113 --> 43:47.531
I want you to say it,
just say it.

43:47.531 --> 43:48.782
It rests on you.

43:48.782 --> 43:50.117
No, this doesn't
rest on me.

43:50.117 --> 43:51.653
This rests on you.

43:51.653 --> 43:52.753
This rests on you.

43:52.753 --> 43:54.238
Now, you say it. You say...

43:54.238 --> 43:56.373
It's up to you now.
No, it's not on me.

43:56.373 --> 43:57.574
You st--

43:57.574 --> 43:59.143
You stay with me.

43:59.143 --> 44:00.978
Look at me. Look at me.

44:00.978 --> 44:04.148
Look at me.

44:04.148 --> 44:06.400
Look at me.

44:24.602 --> 44:26.270
This is yours.

44:27.571 --> 44:29.373
This isn't on me.

44:32.293 --> 44:35.179
This isn't on me!
God damn it!

44:37.265 --> 44:39.350
I can't do this!

44:58.069 --> 45:01.505
[ flies buzzing ]

46:57.322 --> 47:01.541
[ no audible dialogue ]

47:11.985 --> 47:13.887
[ dialing ]

47:16.123 --> 47:18.692
[ line ringing ]

47:19.860 --> 47:21.695
[ ringing ]

47:22.946 --> 47:25.266
[ ringing ]

47:25.266 --> 47:27.835
Hey, it's Angie.
You know what to do.

47:27.835 --> 47:29.670
[ beep ]

47:44.985 --> 47:46.487
[ speaking Zulu ]

47:46.487 --> 47:47.705
Give me your wallet.

47:47.705 --> 47:48.906
I said
give me your wallet!

47:48.906 --> 47:49.907
Get out of here.

47:49.907 --> 47:51.375
Listen here,

47:51.375 --> 47:53.828
give me your wallet
or I'll stick you, man.

47:53.828 --> 47:57.064
Hey! Hey!
Are you deaf?

47:58.966 --> 48:00.301
Get out of here.

48:00.301 --> 48:02.870
This is your chance.
Now go.

48:17.034 --> 48:20.304
[ cell phone ringing ]

48:21.272 --> 48:24.541
[ ringing ]

48:26.410 --> 48:27.911
[ ringing ]

48:27.911 --> 48:29.546
[ beep ]

48:29.546 --> 48:31.983
SMITH:
We just picked up
a call to 911

48:31.983 --> 48:34.385
about a dead woman
in a parking garage.

48:34.385 --> 48:36.453
Caller
sounded distressed.

48:36.453 --> 48:39.556
You feeling
any better now?

48:39.556 --> 48:42.526
So how much
did our friend,
Rachel Shabangu,

48:42.526 --> 48:44.228
tell you
before she died?

48:44.228 --> 48:45.630
You killed her.

48:45.630 --> 48:48.132
Hey, hey, hey,
easy there, big boy.

48:48.132 --> 48:50.467
[ speaking
Afrikaans ]

48:50.467 --> 48:52.670
Look, Michael,
I'm not the one

48:52.670 --> 48:54.538
just out of jail
for hit and run,
okay?

48:54.538 --> 48:58.142
It was an accident,
and I paid my dues.

48:58.142 --> 48:59.677
You don't know me.

48:59.677 --> 49:02.613
You do seem to have
a bit of a knack

49:02.613 --> 49:05.416
at being
in the wrong place
at the wrong time,

49:05.416 --> 49:09.487
don't you, Mr. Woods?

49:09.487 --> 49:13.891
Anyway,
here's the situation.

49:13.891 --> 49:16.394
You've broken
your parole conditions,

49:16.394 --> 49:18.296
making you
a wanted felon.

49:18.296 --> 49:21.582
You're alone
in a city you've
never been to before,

49:21.582 --> 49:23.901
whereas I,
on the other hand,

49:23.901 --> 49:27.355
have access
to the entire
police force here.

49:27.355 --> 49:29.373
I know
the car you're in.

49:29.373 --> 49:31.859
I know its color,
its plates.

49:31.859 --> 49:34.845
I also have
people waiting
for your ex-wife

49:34.845 --> 49:37.581
to take one step
out of that embassy.

49:37.581 --> 49:39.583
One step,
and she's mine.

49:39.583 --> 49:41.719
So what
are you gonna do?

49:41.719 --> 49:44.888
[ chuckles ]
There is one more thing

49:44.888 --> 49:48.392
I thought
might help you make
the right choice here.

49:48.392 --> 49:50.861
Why don't you
turn on your radio?

49:55.800 --> 49:58.268
FEMALE REPORTER:
...and have released his picture

49:58.268 --> 49:59.570
and name to the media.

49:59.570 --> 50:02.540
American Michael Woods
is wanted for the murder

50:02.540 --> 50:03.674
of National Prosecutor
Rachel Shabangu...

50:03.674 --> 50:08.045
[ Smith laughing ]

50:08.045 --> 50:10.981
So let's say you make
the enlightened
choice here

50:10.981 --> 50:13.217
and just stay
out of my way, okay?

50:13.217 --> 50:15.753
[ laughs ]

50:20.057 --> 50:22.993
Cookie boy.

50:22.993 --> 50:25.796
What?

50:25.796 --> 50:29.099
That's what my father
used to always call me,
Cookie boy.

50:30.400 --> 50:32.737
Said I'd always crack
under pressure.

50:34.004 --> 50:36.707
Said I'd always crumble
like a cookie.

50:39.009 --> 50:40.945
He was a mean bastard.

50:40.945 --> 50:43.480
Tough life, huh?

50:43.480 --> 50:45.015
[ chuckles ]

50:45.015 --> 50:48.586
You know,
that chuckle of yours,

50:48.586 --> 50:50.487
it reminds me of him,

50:50.487 --> 50:53.523
'cause he had one
just like it,

50:53.523 --> 50:55.960
