01:06:06.969 --> 01:06:08.438
You, stay put!

01:06:10.072 --> 01:06:12.008
[ siren ]

01:06:24.187 --> 01:06:25.605
[ line ringing ]

01:06:25.605 --> 01:06:27.273
JUDGE MZUKA:
What happened?

