Hello? Can you hear me?

01:07:00.372 --> 01:07:01.741
Hello?

01:07:04.361 --> 01:07:05.912
Oh, God.

01:07:09.348 --> 01:07:10.884
Where is it?

01:07:11.951 --> 01:07:13.152
Come on!

01:07:15.772 --> 01:07:18.742
Come on, please,
please, please, please.

