[ beep beep ]

01:07:31.037 --> 01:07:32.104
No, come on!

01:07:32.104 --> 01:07:33.522
Damn it!

01:07:33.522 --> 01:07:35.925
Damn it all! Come on! Work!

01:07:38.361 --> 01:07:41.480
Burn it all away.

01:07:59.598 --> 01:08:01.534
I'm going in.

